item.title: CVE-2018-11078|2024-08-05T07:54:36.589Z -- dell%20emc -- vplex%20software%3A%20geosynchrony
item.description: Dell EMC VPlex GeoSynchrony, versions prior to 6.1, contains an Insecure File Permissions vulnerability. A remote authenticated malicious user could read from VPN configuration files on and potentially author a MITM attack on the VPN traffic.
